text.tspan: Change in share of countries having achieved different milestones in
Percentage of sovereign countries in each year that completed different milestones in women's political representation.
Source: OWID Women’s Political Representation using Paxton et al (2006), IPU & WDI (2017)
Note: Universal suffrage and share of women in parliament are independent milestones. In some countries the first female MP was elected
before right to vote was granted to all women.
